ss=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h4><b>Lesson Summary</b></h4></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"DmlWZ\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list paragraph, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"editable p-asset ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\"><b>Let us summarize our learning from the module&nbsp;Leading Organizational Development,</b></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"ZSfPi\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   ui-resizable border\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None ng-touched\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\">The organization is a collection of <b>interacting and interdependent individuals</b> who work towards <b>common goals</b> and whose relationships get determined according to a <b>specific structure</b>.</li><li class=\"\">Dimensions of organizational structure include <b>specialization, standardization, formalization, centralization, configuration, and traditionalism</b>.</li><li class=\"\">The four underlying dimensions of the<b> organizational structure</b> are <b>structuring activities</b>, <b>the concentration of authority, line control of the workforce, </b>and <b>the supportive component.&nbsp;</b></li><li class=\"\">By identifying your <b>customers</b>, you can understand their <b>needs </b>and <b>determine</b> whether your<b> product or service</b> will meet them.<br></li><li class=\"\"><b>Communication </b>with customers defines how you <b>progress in your business.</b><br></li><li class=\"\">Running a <b>business </b>requires that you become a <b>jack of all trades</b>. Therefore, it is vital to know the skills you have early on.<br></li><li class=\"\"><b>Marketing </b>is the process of getting <b>clients or customers interested in your products and services.</b><br></li><li class=\"\"><b>Group cohesiveness</b> is a bond that <b>attracts people</b> toward a particular <b>group </b>and <b>resists separation</b> from that group.</li></ul></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n"]}